'============================================================
' AI-Adaptive Trading Bot — UML Diagrams (DETAILED set)
' Regenerated to match the current architecture.
'   * core/ orchestration layer (services + factories + bootstrap + validator)
'   * CompositeStrategy / StrategySlot + regime detectors
'   * sentiment now ADJUSTS MARGIN (IMarginAdjuster), no longer gates signals
'   * live stack: BinanceBroker / DryBroker, LiveSupervisor, PositionStore,
'     RejectionCounter, MarkPriceTickStreamer, LiveMetrics, TelegramNotifier
'   * Backtest scoring / cross-validation pipeline
'============================================================

@startuml Package_Overview
!theme cerulean-outline
title <size:20>**AI-Adaptive Trading Bot**</size>\n<size:14>Proje Paket Diyagramı</size>

